How Defy took — stole 1.7 million dollars from over 50 different youtubers. Now I could never put to justice how MatPat explains this, so just watch the video. This is the second part to it, in the description of this video is should be a link the first. Please spread the word about what had happened because it is jacked up and not okay.

It doesn’t matter whether or not it won’t fit in with you blog, this is important. Please spread the word about this. Make your own post, or just reblog this. I could not care less which you do. If have a bigger following(very unlike me) make your own post about this, because this is important. Lots of youtubers need an MCN to do what they do. Now I don’t want to explain this wrong, because Chuck knows I will, so just watch MatPats videos about them. Please.
